query:
SELECT wl.id, wl.sessionId, wl.studentId, wl.trainingDate, wl.status, s.status as session_status
FROM workout_logs wl
LEFT JOIN sessions s ON s.id = wl.sessionId
ORDER BY wl.createdAt DESC
LIMIT 5;
